text.tspan: Dear {{inv.1.first_names}},
To access content on our website, please visit:
http://wedding.example.org/rsvp/{{inv.1.invite_code}}/
Your invite code for logging into our website is:
{{inv.1.invite_code}}
Please keep this card for future reference.
At our website, you will be able to:
* check or update your RSVP status and meal choices *
* update contact information *
* obtain information about transportation and hotel room blocks *
* get suggestions for things to do when visiting from out-of-town *
* see photos following the wedding and receptions *
If you have questions, please email us at ab@example.org
(or at ben@example.org and aphacker@example.org)
or call us at 617-623-0369.
Love and best wishes,
Alyssa and Ben
